akfishcondition 4.2.2 (September 17, 2025)
----------------------------------------------------------------

DATA UPDATE

- Added 2025 NBS stratum-biomass-weighted condition indicators.


akfishcondition 4.2.1 (August 26, 2025)
----------------------------------------------------------------

BUG FIX

- Fixed poststratify_goa_hauls() paths to match akgfmaps 
  release. 
  
DATA UPDATE

- Added 2025 EBS and GOA stratum-biomass-weighted condition 
  indicators.
- stratum and inpfc_stratum field names for condition indicators
  changed to area_id to match GAP_PRODUCTS AREA_ID names.
  

akfishcondition 4.2.0 (March 21, 2025)
----------------------------------------------------------------

FUNCTIONALITY CHANGES

- get_condition_data(): replaced most SQL queries with gapindex 
  functions wherever possible.
- set_stratum_order(): uses NMFS areas instead of INPFC 
  subareas.
- GOA length-weight samples and biomass are now post-stratified 
  based on 2025 GOA survey design boundaries. Subarea indicators 
  and trends are calculated by NMFS area (610, 620, 630, 640, 
  650).
  
DATA UPDATE

- Condition indicator recalculated to reflect subarea boundaries
  in GOA 2025 survey design.
  

akfishcondition 4.1.3 (October 9, 2024)
----------------------------------------------------------------

BUG FIX

- Fix bug in bias_correction and outlier_rm arguments to 
  calc_lw_residuals().



akfishcondition 4.1.2 (September 25, 2024)
----------------------------------------------------------------

DATA UPDATE

- Updated condition indicator time series with 2024 EBS and AI 
  survey data.
